### Welcome to  my GitHub Page.
Hello and Welcome to my Page!
This page, ported from my GitHub is an easy way to share programming solutions to everyday life or even just for general learning.
Poke around and see what treasures you can find. Just playing, It's just a collection of code for simple projects. You can download the content folders to see what's inside.  

### Like what you see?
If you like what you find here, It would make my day merrier is you leave me a shout out at my github [page](https://github.com/omenta). You can also become a contributor to my page. It will be a pleaser to learn what you have to share. Thank you!
